3
0:00:14.666,000 --> 0:00:17,000
TIC-tat, TIC-tat, TIC-tat TIC-tat, TIC-tat, TIC-tat

4
0:00:18.593,000 --> 0:00:19,000
Sinon, vous entendrez :

5
